Trade/Device Name(s): Safety Blood Collection Set with Holder
Submitter Information: Jiangsu Kangbao Medical Equipment Co., Ltd
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for Jiangsu Kangbao blood collection and infusion sets including safety and standard winged sets, needle holders, and blood collection sets for venous blood collection and short-term IV infusion.
Indications for Use Summary: Intended for venous blood collection and/or short-term infusion of intravenous fluids (2 hours or less), used by trained healthcare professionals with optional safety features to aid in protection against accidental needle stick injury.
